<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />Extend your covenant faithfulness fully to those who know you,</para>

<para style="q1">your defense to the upright of heart.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />Do not let the foot of the arrogant man come near to me.</para>

<para style="q1">Do not let the hand of the wicked drive me away.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />Over there the evildoers have fallen;</para>

<para style="q1">they are knocked down and are not able to get up.</para>
